data.description: Haddon Twp - Westmont Location. Beautiful corner lot property with a two car detached garage.  Home has 3 Bedrooms and 2 Bathrooms, Living Room, Formal Dining Room and Large Kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counter top space. Lower Level is set up to be finished family room with freestanding woodstove, separate office and large laundry room.  Home is also equipped with a Tesla Solar Panel System. Buyer will be responsible for any reactivations. Don't let this one pass you by. Buyer to verify all information prior to bidding. Go to website for more information or to place a bid. Buyer is responsible for their own investigative information on SqFt of home, Room Sizes, Bathroom counts, taxes and all other information regarding this home. This home is a AS-IS Sale with buyer being responsible for all inspections and repairs including CO, final water and sewer and other township inspections. Availability and status of sale type are subject to change at any time.  Owner Occupant 1st Time Purchasers may be eligible for up to $10,000.00 Grant. You can get into this home for less than getting into a rental.  For additional information contact the agent of your choice or click  Agent tab you feel would have the most information in requested information.
